#, fuzzy
msgid "build.gradle"
msgstr "build.gradle"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-panache-next.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You also have to configure the Hibernate processor, which is required:"
msgstr "Você também precisa configurar o processador do Hibernate, o que é obrigatório:"

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-panache-next.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can use any of the xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#setting-up-and-configuring-hibernate-orm[supported JDBC drivers]."
msgstr "Você pode utilizar qualquer um dos xref:hibernate-orm.adoc#setting-up-and-configuring-hibernate-orm[drivers JDBC compatíveis] ."

#. type: Plain text
#. mt: deepl
#: _versions/3.34/guides/hibernate-panache-next.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Make sure you configure your datasource in your `application.properties` (although you don't have to in DEV\n"
